{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Tempo-synced delay with pitch-shifted harmonized echoes.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Port of igorski's Rechoir VST (https://github.com/igorski/rechoir)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Tempo-synced delay (quantized to 16th notes)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Pitch shifting (\u177 ?1 octave)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 7 musical scales for harmonization\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Square wave LFOs (tempo-synced modulation)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Independent stereo modulation (Odd/Even channels)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Freeze mode with reverb\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Lowpass filter with resonance\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Bit reduction/decimator\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Original VST by igorski JSFX port by citizenkeith\par}
